Entries.default: "Looks like the tree took a real liking to him."
"These trees have an ill will. Perhaps it is best to stay in the water."
"The plants have minds of their own, I say. And sharp teeth."
"Makes me regret all those times I told Kana to eat his vegetables."
"If I get snared, don't leave me behind. Please."
"A lesson here. Be screwing a place long enough, it starts to screw back."
